I have no joke being watching family guy nightly for well over 10 years I’ve seen every episode over 100 times at least. It’s my comfort show, I’ve watched it for years with my brother before he passed and I still hear his laugh when I watch it. I’ve watched with every important person in my life. Who knew a tv show could be such a big part of my life and be so impactful. I’m sure I will outlive Seth but I hope this show goes on as long as possible, I’m sure I’ll rewatch episodes until the day I die. Thank you for so much laughter and joy over the years❤️
